# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ClawAgents Configuration (v6.2.1)
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys.
#   cp .env.example .env
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Provider Selection ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Options: "openai", "gemini", or "anthropic". Auto-detected from API keys if omitted.
# PROVIDER=openai

# ─── OpenAI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5-mini

# ─── Azure OpenAI (uncomment all four) ───────────────────────────
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-azure-key
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://YOUR_RESOURCE.openai.azure.com/
# OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-12-01-preview
# OPENAI_API_TYPE=azure

# ─── Local Model: Ollama / vLLM / LM Studio ─────────────────────
# No API key needed — just set model + base_url
# OPENAI_MODEL=llama3.1
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1

# ─── Google Gemini ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-3-flash-preview

# ─── Anthropic Claude ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5

# ─── Advisor Model (optional — pair a smarter model for guidance) ─
# The agent consults the advisor 2-3 times per task: before planning,
# when stuck, and before finishing. Cross-provider supported.
# ADVISOR_MODEL=gpt-5.4                # Stronger model (any provider)
# ADVISOR_API_KEY=sk-...               # Only if different provider than executor
# ADVISOR_MAX_CALLS=3                  # Max consultations per task (default: 3)

# ─── LLM Tuning ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
STREAMING=1                          # 1 = streaming on, 0 = off
CONTEXT_WINDOW=1000000               # Token budget (compacts older messages when exceeded)
MAX_TOKENS=8192                      # Max output tokens per response
TEMPERATURE=0                        # Sampling temp (auto-overridden: GPT-5→1, o1/o3→1)
MAX_ITERATIONS=200                   # Max tool rounds before agent stops

# ─── Trajectory & PTRL (all optional, off by default) ────────────
# CLAW_TRAJECTORY=1                  # Log every turn + score each run
# CLAW_RETHINK=1                     # Inject "rethink" after consecutive failures
# CLAW_LEARN=1                       # Full PTRL: lessons, LLM-as-Judge, thinking tokens
# CLAW_LEARN_MODEL=                  # Separate model for lesson extraction (optional)
# CLAW_PREVIEW_CHARS=120             # Max chars for tool-output previews in logs
# CLAW_RESPONSE_CHARS=500            # Max chars for LLM response text in logs
# CLAW_TIMEOUT=0                     # Global timeout in seconds (0 = no timeout)

# ─── Gateway Server ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# GATEWAY_API_KEY=                   # Set to require Bearer auth on POST endpoints
# GATEWAY_HOST=127.0.0.1             # Bind address (default 127.0.0.1 / loopback only).
                                     # Set to 0.0.0.0 to expose on LAN — REQUIRES GATEWAY_API_KEY
                                     # or you'll get a loud warning at startup.
# GATEWAY_CORS_ORIGINS=*             # Comma-separated list of allowed CORS origins

# ─── web_fetch Tool (SSRF protection) ────────────────────────────
# CLAWAGENTS_WEB_ALLOW_PRIVATE=0     # 1 = allow web_fetch to hit loopback / RFC1918 / link-local
                                     # IPs (dev environments). Default refuses them to prevent
                                     # SSRF (e.g. cloud metadata at 169.254.169.254).

# ─── Messaging Channels (auto-detected by --serve) ──────────────
# Uncomment any channel to auto-start it when running: clawagents --serve
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABC-DEF...       # Telegram bot (get from @BotFather)
# WHATSAPP_AUTH_DIR=.whatsapp-auth           # WhatsApp via Baileys (QR pairing)
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://graph.facebook.com/v21.0  # WhatsApp Business API (alt)
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=EAAx...                 # WhatsApp Business API token
# WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID=123456789                # WhatsApp Business phone number ID
# SIGNAL_ACCOUNT=+1234567890                 # Signal (requires signal-cli)
# SIGNAL_CLI_BIN=signal-cli                  # Path to signal-cli binary
# CHANNEL_DEBOUNCE_MS=500                    # Batch rapid messages within this window

# ─── Env File Override ───────────────────────────────────────────
# CLAWAGENTS_ENV_FILE=/path/to/.env  # Explicit .env path (for CI, Docker, multi-project)


# ─── Claude Code Extra Features ──────────────────────────────────
CLAW_FEATURE_MICRO_COMPACT=1         # 1 = clear old tool result contents; 0 = keep everything
CLAW_FEATURE_FILE_SNAPSHOTS=1        # 1 = copy files to .clawagents/snapshots before writes
CLAW_FEATURE_CACHE_TRACKING=0        # 1 = log detailed API prompt cache stats
CLAW_FEATURE_TYPED_MEMORY=0          # 1 = parse yaml frontmatter in AGENTS.md files
CLAW_FEATURE_WAL=0                   # 1 = persistent write-ahead logging (crash recovery)
CLAW_FEATURE_PERMISSION_RULES=0      # 1 = enforce declarative Allow/Deny bounds (permissions)
CLAW_FEATURE_BACKGROUND_MEMORY=0     # 1 = background task extracting user preferences/state
CLAW_FEATURE_FORKED_AGENTS=0         # 1 = enables run_forked_agent capabilities
CLAW_FEATURE_COORDINATOR=0           # 1 = enables run_coordinator orchestrator mode

# ─── New Features (inspired by claw-code-main) ──────────────────
CLAW_FEATURE_CACHE_BOUNDARY=1        # 1 = split system prompt for Anthropic prompt caching
CLAW_FEATURE_SESSION_PERSISTENCE=0   # 1 = save sessions as JSONL to .clawagents/sessions/
CLAW_FEATURE_ERROR_TAXONOMY=1        # 1 = structured error classification + recovery hints
CLAW_FEATURE_EXTERNAL_HOOKS=0        # 1 = run shell hooks before/after tool calls & LLM calls

# ─── External Hooks (requires CLAW_FEATURE_EXTERNAL_HOOKS=1) ────
# Shell commands that receive JSON on stdin, return JSON on stdout.
# Alternative to .clawagents/hooks.json — env vars take precedence.
# CLAW_HOOK_PRE_TOOL_USE=python guard.py    # Can block or modify tool args
# CLAW_HOOK_POST_TOOL_USE=python log.py     # Can modify tool results
# CLAW_HOOK_PRE_LLM=node inject.js          # Can inject extra messages
# CLAW_HOOK_POST_LLM=node log.js            # Fire-and-forget logging
